This paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically in the area of image manipulation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel architecture that involves generating parameters for image transformation, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves optimization of the network, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the construction of a large-scale dataset, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
